OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FAndy Burnham will formally replace Sir
OL,7,FKeir Starmer as Prime Minister on
OL,8,FMonday.
OL,10,FHe will become the UK's seventh prime
OL,11,Fminister in just over a decade.
OL,13,FMr Burnham became Labour leader on
OL,14,FFriday, after no other candidate put
OL,15,Fthemselves forward
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
