OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1784828906
OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FSir Keir won a landslide at the
OL,7,Fgeneral election in July 2024, but his
OL,8,Fpremiership has been marked by a
OL,9,Fseries of u-turns, controversies and
OL,10,Fsetbacks for Labour, including in
OL,11,Fcouncil elections in the North East in
OL,12,FMay.
OL,14,FHe announced his resignation on 22
OL,15,FJune. That was the same day Mr Burnham
OL,16,Fwas sworn in as an MP after winning a
OL,17,Fby-election in Makerfield, Greater
OL,18,FManchester.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
