PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1784828906
OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FHis time as Mayor of Greater
OL,7,FManchester, and particularly standing
OL,8,Fup to the Conservative government over
OL,9,Ffinancial support during the pandemic,
OL,10,Fearned Andy Burnham the nickname 'King
OL,11,Fof the North.'
OL,13,FIn the House of Commons last week,
OL,14,FHexham Labour MP Joe Morris described
OL,15,Fhim instead as 'King of the North West
OL,16,FMidlands.'
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
