PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1784828906
OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FHe couldn't resist a smile, but he was
OL,7,Falluding to a serious point - about
OL,8,Fthere being a lot north of Manchester,
OL,9,Fand a serious concern - about whether
OL,10,Fthe North East will get its share of
OL,11,Fattention.
OL,13,FMr Burnham has already announced that
OL,14,Fa new, second Prime Minister's office,
OL,15,F'Number 10 North', will be based in
OL,16,Fthe city where he was mayor.
OL,18,FThe Conservative Tees Valley Mayor Ben
OL,19,FHouchen points out that Rishi Sunak,
OL,20,Fwhen he was PM, often worked out of
OL,21,Fthe government offices in Darlington.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
