OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1784828906
OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FHe, and another predecessor Boris
OL,7,FJohnson, talked a lot about 'levelling
OL,8,Fup.'
OL,10,FMr Burnham's ambition to tackle
OL,11,Fregional inequalities is certainly not
OL,12,Fnew, though he'd argue he's more
OL,13,Fserious about it.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
