FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1784828906
OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FIn his speech after becoming Labour
OL,7,Fleader on Friday, he listed Teesside
OL,8,Fwith its steelworks and Tyneside with
OL,9,Fits shipyards among the party
OL,10,Fheartlands that have been
OL,11,Fdeindustrialised and "done down" due
OL,12,Fto the decisions taken by governments
OL,13,Fof all stripes since the 1980s.
OL,15,FHis critics deride him as backward-
OL,16,Flooking.
OL,18,FThe incoming Prime Minister's
OL,19,Fimmediate priority in the present day
OL,20,Fwill be giving people more help with
OL,21,Fthe cost of living.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
