OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1784828906
OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FHis longer-term remedy is handing more
OL,7,Fpower from Westminster to elected
OL,8,Fregional mayors.
OL,10,FWhether devolution actually works
OL,11,Fremains a matter of political debate.
OL,13,FIts supporters often point to Andy
OL,14,FBurnham's own record as the best
OL,15,Fexample of success, and now he wants
OL,16,Fto go further and deeper.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
