SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1784828906
OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FIn our region, Lord Houchen is in post
OL,7,Falongside North East Mayor Kim
OL,8,FMcGuiness, and York and North
OL,9,FYorkshire Mayor David Smith - the
OL,10,Flatter two both Labour politicians.
OL,12,FIt seems they will be entrusted with
OL,13,Fmore funding and responsibility,
OL,14,Fthough for exactly what and how is not
OL,15,Fyet clear. Mr Burnham's aim is to
OL,16,Fsecure what he's described as "good
OL,17,Fgrowth in every postcode" and - not to
OL,18,Funderstate his ambition - also "hope
OL,19,Fin every heart."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
