PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1784828906
OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FIn more direct terms, surely the
OL,7,Fregion's most commonly-made request is
OL,8,Ffor the dualling of the A1 in
OL,9,FNorthumberland.
OL,11,FThat Joe Morris remark I mentioned
OL,12,Fcame during a debate about exactly
OL,13,Fthat. Conservative governments
OL,14,Frepeatedly promised to do it, but
OL,15,Ffailed to follow through.
OL,17,FIn 2024, the new Labour government
OL,18,Fcancelled 13 miles of upgrades,
OL,19,Fjudging they didn't represent value
OL,20,Ffor money.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
