PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1784828906
OL,3,CWhat will Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FLocal leaders from different parties
OL,7,Fargue that the work is in fact vital
OL,8,Fto boost the North East's economy, and
OL,9,Fdecades-long demands have become more
OL,10,Furgent following a series of fatal
OL,11,Fcrashes this year.
OL,13,FAndy Burnham has talked about the need
OL,14,Ffor "decent infrastructure in all
OL,15,Fparts of the UK", and many in our
OL,16,Fregion hope his arrival signals the
OL,17,Fgovernment changing its tune on the
OL,18,FA1. That would be concrete evidence of
OL,19,Fa commitment to improving the
OL,20,Fprospects of what some call 'the true
OL,21,Fnorth.'
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/11
